                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/esim/search",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "esim",
                "search"
              ]
            },
            "description": "### Transfer Search\n\nThis endpoint allows you to search for transfer options based on the provided criteria.\n\n#### Request Body\n\n- `segment` (array): An array of segments containing details about the departure and arrival locations, outbound date, and other relevant information.\n    \n    - `departure_type`: The type of departure location (e.g., AIRPORT).\n        \n    - `departure_code`: The code of the departure location (e.g., CUN).\n        \n    - `departure_city`: The city of the departure location (e.g., Q.R.).\n        \n    - `departure_country`: The country of the departure location (e.g., MX).\n        \n    - `arrival_type`: The type of arrival location (e.g., LOC).\n        \n    - `arrival_code`: The code of the arrival location.\n        \n    - `arrival_city`: The city of the arrival location.\n        \n    - `arrival_country`: The country of the arrival location.\n        \n    - `outbound_date`: The date and time of the outbound transfer.\n        \n- `travelers_adult` (number): The number of adult travelers.\n    \n- `travelers_child` (number): The number of child travelers.\n    \n- `travelers_child_age` (array): An array of ages of child travelers.\n    \n- `travelers_infants` (number): The number of infant travelers.\n    \n- `travelers_infants_age` (array): An array of ages of infant travelers.\n    \n- `transfer_type` (string): The type of transfer (e.g., private).\n    \n- `supplier_uid` (string): The unique identifier of the supplier.\n    \n- `partner_id` (string): The partner ID.\n    \n- `short_ref` (string): A short reference.\n    \n- `language` (string): The language preference for the response (e.g., en).\n    \n\n#### Response\n\nThe response will contain the transfer options based on the provided criteria."
          },
          "response": []
        },
